   <h2>Which semester tickets are available so far?</h2>
   <h4>VMT ticket:</h4>
   The VMT ticket allows you to use all means of transport (buses and streetcars) in the VMT area between Gotha and Gera, except those of the Jena local transport and railroad companies.

   <h4>JNV-Ticket:</h4>
   With the JNV ticket, all buses and streetcars of the Jena local transport can be used. In addition, the Anruf-Sammel-Taxen (AST) are already included in the price.

   <h4>Deutsche Bahn ticket (DB-Ticket):</h4>
   With the DB-Ticket, all students in Thuringia can travel on local trains to the last stop in Thuringia. It is also possible to combine the ticket with other state tickets. The ticket is not valid on the routes Eisenach - Gerstungen (Cantus), Obstfelderschmiede - Cursdorf (Oberweißbacher Berg- und Schwarzatalbahn) and Nordhausen - Eisfelder Talmühle (Harzer Schmalspurbahnen).

